Class LongIdMap<T>

java.lang.Object
chav1961.purelib.basic.LongIdMap<T>
Type Parameters:
T - any king of data associated with the tree elements
public class LongIdMap<T>
extends java.lang.Object

This class implements a special king of map, oriented to use with AndOrTree class. It can be also used to manipulate with the identifiers was generated and used by AndOrTree.
